product.name: OptiClean™ All-Purpose Peg Dish Rack 2.5" Pegs

description.html:
• Versatile Pegs – All-purpose peg rack securely holds plates, smaller trays and platters with 1.75” space between .5” pegs
  • Open Design – Open construction promotes even and thorough washing, drying and draining
  • Durable Construction – Double-wall, reinforced plastic is built for many years of heavy use
  • Standard Compatibility – Rack stacks securely with other industry standard warewashing racks
  • Secure Handling – Molded-in handles allow for secure grip and transportation
